			<div class="content" id="post-content-2709301">
									

<p>This is a re-write (in PL GoI-format) of a previous mainlist article - it has changed substantially (albeit not fundamentally) since its earlier incarnation.</p>
<p>Many thanks to the many people who looked this over and offered their thoughts:</p>
<ul>
<li>sirpudding, who still doesn't believe in this type of SRA, but was always ready to share thoughts and lore about how an SRA should really work</li>
<li>Dr Reach, for an amazing interlude on Nornirian Cluster Bombs</li>
<li>dankaar, for coming up with a punchline to end this on</li>
<li>MrWrong and Scorpion451, for finding ways to de-power the anchors, and reminding me to *actually read* what SCP-2000 says, instead of making it up</li>
<li>A Random Day, for useful thoughts about worldbuilding</li>
</ul>
<p>Apologies to those who I've forgotten to credit. Thanks ophite too for providing a reason to rush this prototype to market!</p>

							</div>

								
