														</div>
			</div>
			<div class="content" id="post-content-2709411">
									

<p>Hmmmm&#8230;.</p>
<p>This is a pretty vast improvement over the original post as an SCP article. I think it's a pretty solid exploration, and I was going to complain about your neurological description early on but you got more into detail later, so the science checks out.</p>
<p>You told this story very well, but I can't <em>quite</em> suspend my disbelief about the idea that there are a significant number of reality benders walking around with the same powers and casual mechanism. It just clashes hard with my ideas about the Foundation-verse, and I don't see the problem with heterogeneity addressed here. That's unfortunate, since I like just about everything else.</p>
<p>No vote for now, but I might flip up on reflection.</p>

							</div>

								
					
