<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-630985-1"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-630985-1')">1</a>. Mm, liquefied dead brain matter.</div>
<div class="footnote-footer" id="footnote-630985-2"><a href="javascript:;" onclick="WIKIDOT.page.utils.scrollToReference('footnoteref-630985-2')">2</a>. But still modified, of course.</div>
</div>

